ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-British Virgin Islands - Exchange of information on tax matters ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary, on behalf of Canada, to BRING INTO FORCE the AGREEMENT between the Government of CANADA and the Government of the BRITISH VIRGIN ISLANDS under Entrustment from the Government of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland for the EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION ON TAX MATTERS.
